      <title>克里姆林宮稱核武演習是俄羅斯對西方聲明的回應</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/kremlin-says-nuclear-weapon-drills-are-russias-response-wests-statements-2024-05-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[克里姆林宮週一表示，俄羅斯的戰術核武演習是對西方向烏克蘭派遣軍隊的聲明的回應。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/kremlin-says-nuclear-weapon-drills-are-russias-response-wests-statements-2024-05-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 09:07:24 GMT</pubDate>
